    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but i also hear a lot of people saying that higher wages actually help the local economy because workers have more money to spend at places like my shop. couldnt that prevent the \"death spiral\" of a struggling town?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
